      "review_summary": "The PR adds local-mode `/status` and `/compact` handling in the TUI command switch and adds two focused command-handler tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +10, Tests +26. Total +36 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. with high confidence from source: slash input enters `handleCommand`, local discovery/help expose shared commands, and unhandled names fall through to `sendMessage(raw)` and then `agentCommandFromIngress`. I did not run the local PTY repro because this review is read-only.",
